name: Darwin Rust Server
body:
`net.connect darwin.clanservers.com:28046 `

**Welcome to our Group. **
Our Server Offers 

No Building Decay! 
Friendly to new Players 
Active Admins 

We are working towards building a friendly server that is community based, and would like to keep the PVP aspect of the game. 

`net.connect darwin.clanservers.com:28046` 
or 
`net.connect 108.61.100.146:28046 `
Please use the above net.connect to join and help us build on our island. 

Community suggestions are welcomed and voted upon by group members. 

**Features:** 
-Community driven 

-Friendly to new players 

-Midwest United States (Location) 

-PVP 

-No sleepers 

-Broadcast PvP death messages 

-Chat history 

-Player list & online count 

-Private messaging system 

-Friend system 

-Starter kits 

-Display location coordinates & ping
